e pool bar as you are gazing the serene Aegean blue and breathing the fresh sea breezes is waiting for you at the large swimming pool of Amber Light, one of the largest on the island! Then head to the Spa of Amber Light Villas.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Feel totally rejuvenated in the jacuzzi’s bubbles or the steam of the hammam and arrange a massage session with our therapists. For more beauty treatments book an appointment for manicure and pedicure and feel fabulous during your stay in Amber Light Villas.</span></p>\n<p><b class=\"font-500\">The Services Of Amber Light Villas In Santorini</b></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A range of services aiming to make your stay at Amber Light Villas more relaxing and beautiful are at your disposal. We can arrange exclusively personalized services such as concierge services, restaurant recommendations, cruise bookings and activities proposals. Amber Light’s manager will be by your side from the very first moment of the reservation to the time of your departure.</span></p>\n","css":{"element":"div","class":"main-text-body text-center","color":"primary-white"}}]}]},"3":{"wrapper":{"fluid":false,"css":{"border":"0","backgroundColor":"#FFFFFF"},"class":"d-none d-md-block","rows":[{"css":{"padding":"80px 0 0 0","border":"0"},"columns":{"sizes":["col-md-12  animation--up"]}}]},"rows":[{"columns":[{"items":[{"link":"/","label":"AQUA VISTA HOTELS"},{"link":"/hotels-in-santorini","label":"hotels in santorini"},{"link":"/hotels-in-santorini/amber-light-villas","label":"amber light villas"},{"link":"","label":"facilities"}],"css":{"element":"div","class":"secondary-post-text","color":"primary-dark"}}]}]},"4":{"wrapper":{"fluid":false,"css":{"border":"0","backgroundColor":"#FFFFFF","padding":"80px 0 60px 0"},"rows":[{"css":{"padding":"0 0 60px 0","border":"0","maxWidth":"1440px","margin":"0 auto"},"columns":{"sizes":["col-md-12  animation--up"]}}]},"rows":[{"columns":[{"items":[{"title":"The facilities o